        Connect with licensed & insured professionals in {cityName}.
      </p>
      <a
        href={SITE_CONFIG.phoneHref}
        style="background: #ea580c; color: white !important; padding: 1.2rem; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 12px; font-weight: 900; font-size: clamp(1.3rem, 5vw, 1.8rem); display: block; box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(234, 88, 12, 0.3);"
        >{SITE_CONFIG.phone}</a
      >
    </div>

    <!-- 3 SIMPLE STEPS -->
    <section style="margin-top: 4rem;">
      <h2
        style="color: #064e3b; font-size: 1.8rem; font-weight: 900; text-align: center; margin-bottom: 2rem;"
      >
        3 Simple Steps to Service
      </h2>
      <div
        style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr)); gap: 20px;"
      >
        <div class="info-card-base step-card">
          <div class="icon-box" style="background: #e0f2fe;">üìû</div>
          <h4>1. Call Us</h4>
          <p>Connect with our dispatch office instantly for help.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="info-card-base step-card">
          <div class="icon-box" style="background: #fef3c7;">üìã</div>
          <h4>2. Free Quote</h4>
          <p>Get an expert assessment and no-obligation pricing.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="info-card-base step-card">
          <div class="icon-box" style="background: #dcfce7;">‚úÖ</div>
          <h4>3. Job Done</h4>
          <p>Professional service completed with full property cleanup.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ‚òÖ Dƒ∞NAMƒ∞K YEREL DURUM VE HAVA DURUMU BLOƒûU ‚òÖ -->
    <section
      style="margin-top: 3rem; display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr)); gap: 20px;"
    >
      <!-- SOL KUTU: Hava Durumu Widget'ƒ± -->
      <div
        style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e0f2fe 0%, #f0f9ff 100%); padding: 1.5rem; border-radius: 24px; border: 1px solid #bae6fd; position: relative; overflow: hidden; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between;"
      >
        <div
          style="position: absolute; right: -10px; bottom: -10px; font-size: 5rem; opacity: 0.1; transform: rotate(-15deg);"
        >
          ‚òÄÔ∏è
        </div>
        <div style="position: relative; z-index: 1;">
          <div
            style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; margin-bottom: 5px;"
          >
            <span
              style="background: #0369a1; color: white; font-size: 0.65rem; padding: 2px 8px; border-radius: 50px; font-weight: 800; text-transform: uppercase;"
              >Live Update</span
            >
            <span style="color: #0369a1; font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: 700;"
              >{cityName}, FL</span
            >
          </div>
          <div style="display: flex; align-items: baseline; gap: 5px;">
            <span style="font-size: 2.5rem; font-weight: 900; color: #0c4a6e;"
              >78¬∞F</span
            >
            <span style="font-size: 1rem; color: #0369a1; font-weight: 600;"
              >Sunny</span
            >
          </div>
          <p
            style="margin: 8px 0 0; color: #0c4a6e; font-size: 0.85rem; font-weight: 700; line-height: 1.3;"
          >
            <span style="color: #16a34a;">‚óè</span> Optimal for {
              serviceInfo.name.toLowerCase()
            }
          </p>
        </div>
        <div style="text-align: right; position: relative; z-index: 1;">
          <div
            style="font-size: 3.5rem; filter: drop-shadow(0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.1));"
          >
            üå§Ô∏è
          </div>
          <div
            style="font-size: 0.7rem; color: #0369a1; font-weight: 800; text-transform: uppercase; margin-top: -5px;"
          >
            Florida Skies
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- SAƒû KUTU: Yerel Bilgi Kartƒ± -->
      <div
        style="background: white; padding: 1.5rem; border-radius: 24px; border: 1px solid #eee; box-shadow: 0 10px 25px -5px rgba(0,0,0,0.05); display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center;"
      >
        <div
          style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; margin-bottom: 15px;"
        >
          <div
            style="background: #fff7ed; width: 40px; height: 40px; border-radius: 10px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 1.2rem;"
          >
            üìç
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4
              style="margin: 0; color: #1b4332; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 800;"
            >
              Local Service Hub
            </h4>
            <p
              style="margin: 0; color: #6b7280; font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: 600;"
            >
              {countyName} County Dispatch
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 10px;">
          <div
            style="background: #f8fafc; padding: 10px; border-radius: 12px; border: 1px solid #f1f5f9;"
          >
